short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Feel the power of the Porsche 911 GT with a stunning live wallpaper that brings this iconic car to your Chrome new tab.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Porsche 911 GT Live Wallpaper showcases the sleek design and high performance of this legendary vehicle, giving car enthusiasts a thrilling visual experience every time they open a new tab.

Features:
Porsche 911 GT Live Wallpaper
Google search bar
Addable and removable shortcuts
Date and time display

This Chrome extension enhances your browsing with a dynamic chrome wallpaper and essential tools. As one of the top chrome live wallpapers, it combines style and practicality, transforming your chrome background into a visual treat.

For more exciting live wallpapers, explore Gameograf.com. Discover extensions like: McLaren 570S Live Wallpaper, Ferrari 488 Live Wallpaper, Lamborghini Aventador Live Wallpaper, Bugatti Chiron Live Wallpaper, Aston Martin Vantage Live Wallpaper.
